dotfiles
========

Public dotfiles for sync. This repository doesn't contains packages required to work properly.
Initial setup is required with package manager. Most of my systems use Nix if available.
Check "flake.nix" if you are interested. 

- WindowManager: sway / yabai
- Terminal: kitty, tmux
- Shell: elvish

setup
-----

stow

    git clone -j 8 "https://github.com/aca/dotfiles.git" ~/src/root/dotfiles --recursive --shallow-submodules
    git clone "https://github.com/aca/stow-antifold.git" ~/src/root/stow-antifold
    cd ~/src/root
    stow --adopt -v --target $HOME dotfiles stow-antifold

keys 

    curl -L github.com/aca.keys > ~/.ssh/authorized_keys

local configs

    git clone root:~/src/root/$(hostname -s)

Dev container

    docker run -it acadx0/tools:devcontainer
